What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: I would definitely recommend this class. I have never taken a film class and so have felt nervous to take a class that tests on films, but this was a very good combination of different material and good literature so I learned a lot but students have the option to choose what they write about for the papers so there is flexibility.
I would recommend this to other students. The syllabus is great.
This is a great class. The structure lets you enjoy every reading and Professor Clark is wonderful.
